instructions: Sign in to your Play Console . Click Settings and then Payments Settings .

Find "Payments profile" then find "[your country] tax info" and click Edit . To enter or edit your tax info, click Add tax info or Update tax info . To submit the W-9 to the IRS from within your payments profile, answer the questions, then fill out the W-9 form and click Submit . Answer the questions and click Submit to submit the Certificate of Foreign Status (W-8BEN) to the IRS from within your payments profile. Click Save .
